I've played almost every Kemco JRPG in the store and this one is as fun as the best of them. The story is interesting, if not a little familiar. The graphics are good, as are the music scores and additional support sections. A solid Kemco game that has length and replayability that happens to deliver the usual, expected fair of Guilds, Maids and Levelling. Nice!
